          }
        },
        "testimonial_UGEeMK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_title": "Prezadovoljna,",
            "review_text": "<p>I've been looking for a while for 100% natural skincare products in Sarajevo and I am so grateful to have found this natural line. I got their Prickly Pear & Argan Renewal Face Cream. It gives a lot of moisture and is still rich enough so my skin doesn't feel dry old day. I have a sensitive skin, so while many other product would cause allergy around my eyes or even redness in the face I didn't have this problem with Azourane skincare line. I highly recommend it and will be back to sample more stuff!<br/><br/></p>",
            "customer_name": "Buric",
            "product": "100-arganovo-ulje",
            "product_reference": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_QXhTRh": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_title": "I absolutely love Azourane skincare!",
            "review_text": "<p>The quality exceeded my expectations. Shipping was fast and the packaging was beautiful. Highly recommended.</p>",
            "customer_name": "Vildana E.",
            "product": "afoulki",
            "product_reference": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_NC4JNq": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_title": "Imam jako osjetljivu kožu i...",
            "review_text": "<p>Imam jako osjetljivu kožu i Amaan mi savršeno odgovara – temeljito čisti, ali bez isušivanja. Osjećaj je kao da lice umijem hladnom izvorskom vodom, svako jutro i svako veče.</p>",
            "customer_name": "Sarah J.",
            "product": "amaan",
            "product_reference": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_9AHzFh": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_title": "Prezadovoljna",
            "review_text": "<p>od kada koristim Azourane arganovo ulje, svakodnevno za lice po par kapi , koža je blistava  , nahranjena i hidrirana.</p>",
            "customer_name": "Sarah J.",
