        "review_QxQEY6": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "quote": "I absolutely love Azourane skincare! I've been looking for a while for 100% natural skincare products in Sarajevo and I am so grateful to have found this natural line. I got their Prickly Pear & Argan Renewal Face Cream. It gives a lot of moisture and is still rich enough so my skin doesn't feel dry old day. I have a sensitive skin, so while many other product would cause allergy around my eyes or even redness in the face I didn't have this problem with Azourane skincare line. I highly recommend it and will be back to sample more stuff!",
